        "Given $ d $ bits $b=(b_1, b_2, ... , b_d) \\in \\{0, 1\\}^d$, we define $$XOR(b) = Σ_{i=1}^db_i\\ mod\\ 2$$\n",
        "\n",
        "In this question, you will train a feedforward neural network to model the multidimensional XOR problem.\n",
